---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" headerTitle="Terms of Service">
  <main>
    <section
      id="terms-of-service"
      class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 p-12 rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-12"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100"
      >
        Terms of Service
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-justify">
        Welcome to Freedom Butchers. By accessing and using our website, you
        agree to comply with the following Terms of Service. Please read them
        carefully.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Use of Our Website
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        Our website is available for your personal and commercial use, provided
        you agree to not engage in any activity that may harm our services or
        other users. We reserve the right to terminate access to any user
        violating these terms.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Intellectual Property
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        All content on this site, including text, graphics, logos, images, and
        software, is the property of Freedom Butchers and is protected by
        copyright and other intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce or
        distribute any content without prior written consent.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Ordering and Payments
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        By placing an order on our site, you agree to provide accurate and
        complete information. All payments are securely processed, and we
        reserve the right to cancel any order for any reason, including errors
        in pricing or stock availability.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Refunds and Cancellations
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        We strive to ensure satisfaction with all purchases. However, if you
        wish to request a refund or cancel your order, please contact us within
        24 hours of purchase. Our full refund policy can be found on the Refunds
        page.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Limitation of Liability
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        Freedom Butchers is not responsible for any damages, losses, or claims
        arising from your use of this website or any products purchased, except
        where explicitly required by law.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Changes to Terms
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-justify">
        We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Any changes will
        be posted on this page, and your continued use of the site constitutes
        acceptance of the revised terms.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
        Contact Us
      </h3>
      <p class="text-center text-lg">
        If you have any questions or concerns regarding our Terms of Service,
        please contact us at <a
          href="mailto:contact@freedombutchers.com"
          class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact@freedombutchers.com</a
        >.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
